00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:46.560
[Amit Varma]: Western thought, and proposes and maps out two major strains of Indian conservatism in

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:51.360
[Amit Varma]: a formulation that was both new and thought provoking for me. The conversation you'll

00:03:51.360 --> 00:03:56.160
